channel.title: Jinsanity - PI Totally Redone
channel.description:
Jinrake on R-S j1nrak3 on RL
This is probably the stablest PI to date. Everything has been re-done and there's a lot of unfinished content included.
[B][U]Features:[/U][/B]
[CENTER]- Cache Loading ripped from hyperion - Extreme Stability - Fuckload of content; not even joking! Just needs implementation. - Hyperions game engine - Combat is pretty good just a few bugs; rip from other servers - Nikkis MYSQL Pooling - Immediate Packet processing (Check in Config.java for options...) - Hyperion Task system - Hyperion event system - Hyperion background load system - Everything converted into events - 90% A Star Pathfinding implemented - Perfect Clan Chat - In-game highscored implemented - Michael bulls tick system - Achievement System (100% Working and 100% Customizable) - Packets re-done, error free - Nearly all skills re-done - NPC+Player updating procedures re-done - NPC Region processing - Regions from Hyperion implemented - Apparently loads of dupes; fix them yourself i've done enough - Bank pins - Curses implementation - Double XP Weekend auto-checker (runs on a separate thread; no sync issues) - God Books making - Enchanting (Core?) - Premium System - Poison your own weapon system (CRS) - Spirit Shield making - Perk System - Custom teleport system - Auto-trainer system - Genie lamp - Set Skills system - Treasure Trail system - Combat max hits redone - In game highscores system [stable+optimized] - Barrows - Castle Wars - Damage Wars - Fight Caves - Fight Pits - Free For All - Invasion - Mage Arena - Pest Control w/NPCS - Onslaught - War - Warriors Guild - Bounty Hunter - Clan Wars - Challengers Torturement - Killzone - Lottery - Zombies [100% working, great minigame] - Party Room - Player Owned Shops - PvP Planet Market - The PvP aspect of this server is FUCKING AMAZING. - Artefacts - PvP Drops work 100% like runescape, drops dumped in PvPDropConfig.java file - Great formula to calculate success rate in PvP Drops - Massacre System - KillStreaks - Clan kills/deaths/kd/points - Pk Points - Quest tab information - Loads of Registered sounds added - Combat sounds - NPC Sounds - World Sounds - Obelisks redone - Teletabs - No warnings on Eclipse - No errors - No Anti-leech[/CENTER]
Wait; this IS the stablest PI; GenericX held ~300 no lagg using this base.
Download Link: [url=http://jinrake.info/index.php?page=jinsanity]Download Jinsanity[/url]
[B][U]Credits:[/U][/B] Hyperion team - 50% Jinrake - 30% Sanity - 10% Others - 10%
